  "faqs": [
    {
      "q": "Which AI video tool has a free plan?",
      "a": "All 6 tools offer free plans. HeyGen and Synthesia provide free credits for avatar videos. Runway, Pika, Sora, and Kling offer free tiers for AI video generation with limited credits and watermark."
    },
    {
      "q": "What is the cheapest AI video tool?",
      "a": "Runway Standard at $12/month offers the most affordable paid plan. Pika Basic at $10/month and Kling Plus at $10/month are also budget-friendly options for basic AI video generation."
    },
    {
      "q": "Which AI video tool has the best quality?",
      "a": "It depends on use case. For avatar videos, HeyGen leads in realism. For creative video generation, Runway and Pika produce high-quality outputs. Sora excels in physics simulation and realism."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I use AI video tools commercially?",
      "a": "Most paid plans allow commercial use. Free plans usually have restrictions and watermarks. Check each tool's license terms for specific usage rights."
    },
    {
      "q": "Do these tools offer API access?",
      "a": "HeyGen, Synthesia, Runway, and Kling offer API access (usually on Business/Enterprise plans). Pika has limited API. Sora does not currently offer public API access."
    }
  ]
